<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Your Matched Advisors</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f3f4f6; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2937;">
    <div style="padding: 32px 16px;">
      <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0;">
        <tr>
          <td style="background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 24px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);">
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%" style="border-collapse: collapse;">
              <tr>
                <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #eef2ff 0%, #f0fdf4 100%); padding: 32px 36px;">
                  <p style="margin: 0; color: #6366f1; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase;">Your Match Summary</p>
                  <h1 style="margin: 10px 0 6px; font-size: 24px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;">{{sellerName}}, here are your top advisor matches</h1>
                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6;">
                    You are matched with these {{advisorCount}} advisor{{pluralLabel}}. Their contact details and key highlights are below so you can start conversations right away.
                  </p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td style="padding: 24px 32px 16px;">
                  <div style="background-color: #eef2ff; border: 1px solid #c7d2fe; border-radius: 16px; padding: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: center;">
                    <p style="margin: 0; color: #4338ca; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;">Advisor Chooser Match: The seller has opted to reach out directly.</p>
                  </div>

                  <div style="display: block;">
                    {{advisorList}}
                  </div>

                  <div style="background-color: #f9fafb; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-radius: 18px; padding: 22px; margin: 24px 0 12px;">
                    <h2 style="margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 18px; color: #111827;">Next steps</h2>
                    <ol style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #4b5563; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7;">
                      <li>We sent you an email with questions that you should ask an Advisor and questions you should expect to answer. Check your inbox or spam folder.</li>
                      <li>If you asked us to make introductions - check your inbox or spam.</li>
                      <li> Reach out directly to Advisors that you think could help your company. Let them know we sent you!</li>
                      <li>If you didn't delete your profile, you can log back into AdvisorChooser.com with your email for the next 24 hours to continue where you left off.  Otherwise, feel free to come back anytime and use Advisor Chooser again</li>
                    </ol>
                  </div>

                  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">Questions? Email support@advisorchooser.com anytime.</p>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>

      <p style="margin: 24px auto 0; max-width: 720px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
        This email contains confidential advisor information you requested from the Advisor Chooser Platform.
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
